OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLiving near Sure Start     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fboosted GCSEs - study      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Children from low-income families who  
OL,6, grew up near a Sure Start centre did   
OL,7, better than their peers at GCSEs, says 
OL,8, the Institute for Fiscal Studies (IFS).
OL,10,FIts research says those living near a  
OL,11,Fcentre performed up to three grades    
OL,12,Fbetter than those further away.        
OL,14,FSure Start centres started in 1998 to  
OL,15,Fgive parents of toddlers extra support,
OL,16,Fespecially in disadvantaged areas, but 
OL,17,Fmany have closed.                      
OL,19,FThe Department for Education has been  
OL,20,Fapproached for comment.                
